      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Engines\" title=\"Engines\">Engines</a> * Deuterium</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/File:Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg/330px-Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"100\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg/500px-Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg 1.5x, https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/e5/Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg/960px-Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Deuterium_discharge_tube.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Deuterium <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gas-filled_tube\">discharge tube</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Deuterium</b>,<br />\nan <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compatible chess engine by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, initially based on <a href=\"/TSCP\" title=\"TSCP\">TSCP</a> or Tom's Simple Chess Program by <a href=\"/Tom_Kerrigan\" title=\"Tom Kerrigan\">Tom Kerrigan</a>.\nWith version 14.2.33.276, released in June 2014, the former <a href=\"/Chess_Engine_Communication_Protocol\" title=\"Chess Engine Communication Protocol\">Chess Engine Communication Protocol</a> compliance was superseded by <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Features\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Features</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Board_Representation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Board Representation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Search\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Search</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Evaluation\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Evaluation</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Misc\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#Tournament_Play\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tournament Play</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Selected_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Games</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#2009\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2009</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-13\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-14\"><a href=\"#Chess_Engine\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Engine</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-15\"><a href=\"#Misc_2\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Misc</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-16\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Features\">Features</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Features\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Board_Representation\"><a href=\"/Board_Representation\" title=\"Board Representation\">Board Representation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Board Representation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/8x8_Board\" title=\"8x8 Board\">8x8 Board</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Lists\" title=\"Piece-Lists\">Piece-Lists</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Search\"><a href=\"/Search\" title=\"Search\">Search</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Search\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Iterative_Deepening\" title=\"Iterative Deepening\">Iterative Deepening</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Aspiration_Windows\" title=\"Aspiration Windows\">Aspiration Windows</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Fail-Soft\" title=\"Fail-Soft\">Fail-Soft</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/NegaScout\" title=\"NegaScout\">NegaScout</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Selectivity\" title=\"Selectivity\">Selectivity</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Null_Move_Pruning\" title=\"Null Move Pruning\">Null Move Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Leaf_Pruning\" title=\"History Leaf Pruning\">Move History/Statistics Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Futility_Pruning\" title=\"Futility Pruning\">Futility Pruning</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Late_Move_Reductions\" title=\"Late Move Reductions\">Late Move Reductions</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Razoring\" title=\"Razoring\">Razoring</a></li></ul></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Move_Ordering\" title=\"Move Ordering\">Move Ordering</a>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Static_Exchange_Evaluation\" title=\"Static Exchange Evaluation\">Static Exchange Evaluation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Killer_Heuristic\" title=\"Killer Heuristic\">Killer Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Countermove_Heuristic\" title=\"Countermove Heuristic\">Countermove Heuristic</a></li></ul></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Evaluation\"><a href=\"/Evaluation\" title=\"Evaluation\">Evaluation</a></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Evaluation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Material\" title=\"Material\">Material</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Evaluation_Hash_Table\" title=\"Evaluation Hash Table\">Evaluation Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Piece-Square_Tables\" title=\"Piece-Square Tables\">Piece-Square Tables</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Structure\" title=\"Pawn Structure\">Pawn Structure</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Pawn_Hash_Table\" title=\"Pawn Hash Table\">Pawn Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Outposts\" title=\"Outposts\">Outposts</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mobility\" title=\"Mobility\">Mobility</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/King_Safety\" title=\"King Safety\">King Safety</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/PolyGlot\" title=\"PolyGlot\">PolyGlot Opening Book</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Scorpio_Bitbases\" title=\"Scorpio Bitbases\">6-men Scorpio Bitbases</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Tournament_Play\">Tournament Play</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Tournament Play\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Deuterium participated at most <a href=\"/ACCA_World_Computer_Rapid_Chess_Championship\" title=\"ACCA World Computer Rapid Chess Championship\">ACCA World Computer Rapid Chess Championships</a>, first in <a href=\"/WCRCC_2007\" title=\"WCRCC 2007\">2007</a>, as well as most recent <a href=\"/CCT_Tournaments\" title=\"CCT Tournaments\">CCT Tournaments</a> since <a href=\"/CCT11\" title=\"CCT11\">CCT11</a>. Over the board, Deuterium became third at the <a href=\"/CCC_2009\" title=\"CCC 2009\">CCC 2009</a> 4th Chess Computer Cup in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carugate\">Carugate</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Italy\">Italy</a>, where it also played the <a href=\"/IOCSC_2010\" title=\"IOCSC 2010\">1st Italian Open Chess Software Cup</a> in 2010. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Games\">Selected Games</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Games\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><a href=\"/CCT14\" title=\"CCT14\">CCT14</a>, round 5, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Deuterium</a> - <a href=\"/Pandix\" title=\"Pandix\">Pandix</a>\n</p>\n<pre>\n[Event \"CCT14\"]\n[Site \"Internet Chess Club\"]\n[Date \"2012.02.26\"]\n[Round \"5\"]\n[White \"Deuterium\"]\n[Black \"Pandix\"]\n[Result \"1/2-1/2\"]\n\n1.d4 Nf6 2.c4 e6 3.Nf3 d5 4.Nc3 Be7 5.Bg5 O-O 6.e3 h6 7.Bh4 b6 8.Be2 Bb7 \n9.Bxf6 Bxf6 10.cxd5 exd5 11.b4 c6 12.O-O Qd6 13.a3 Be7 14.Bd3 a5 15.b5 c5 \n16.e4 Nd7 17.Re1 cxd4 18.Nxd4 Bf6 19.Nf5 Qe5 20.Nxd5 Qxa1 21.Nxh6+ Kh8 \n22.Nxf7+ Kg8 23.Nh6+ Kh8 24.Nf7+ Kg8 25.Nh6+ Kh8 26.Nf7+ 1/2-1/2\n</pre>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=8\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2009\">2009</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=9\" title=\"Edit section: 2009\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=31177\">Deuterium</a> by <a href=\"/Swaminathan_Natarajan\" title=\"Swaminathan Natarajan\">Swaminathan Natarajan</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 21, 2009&#160;» <a href=\"/Strategic_Test_Suite\" title=\"Strategic Test Suite\">Strategic Test Suite</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=31177&amp;start=7\">Re: Deuterium</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 23, 2009</dd></dl>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=10\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=35476\">WCRCC 2010 - Deuterium Games</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 17, 2010&#160;» <a href=\"/WCRCC_2010\" title=\"WCRCC 2010\">WCRCC 2010</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=36716\">Deuterium v10.01.27.213 Released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 15, 2010</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=38672\">Deuterium v11.01.28.159 released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 06, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=39848\">2011 Fifth Annual ACCA WCRCC: Deuterium games</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 24, 2011&#160;» <a href=\"/WCRCC_2011\" title=\"WCRCC 2011\">WCRCC 2011</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=41450\">Deuterium update and other engines</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 14, 2011</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=48912\">Deuterium v13.1.31.113 released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 10, 2013</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=52710\">Deuterium v14.2.33.276 released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 21, 2014</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=55115\">Nirvanachess, Deuterium and EXchess are on the way!</a> by <a href=\"/Frank_Quisinsky\" title=\"Frank Quisinsky\">Frank Quisinsky</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 27, 2015</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=67578\">Deuterium 2018 released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 27, 2018</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69721\">Deuterium v2019.1 released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, January 25, 2019</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=71875\">Deuterium released</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 21, 2019</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75104\">Yet another parameter tuner using optuna framework</a> by <a href=\"/Ferdinand_Mosca\" title=\"Ferdinand Mosca\">Ferdinand Mosca</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 14, 2020&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=13\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Engine\">Chess Engine</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=14\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Engine\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/view/deuterium-chess/home\">Deuterium Chess</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://sites.google.com/site/deuteriumengine/\">Deuterium Homepage</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://github.com/fsmosca/Optuna-Game-Parameter-Tuner\">GitHub - fsmosca/Optuna-Game-Parameter-Tuner: A game search and evaluation parameter tuner using optuna framework</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Automated_Tuning\" title=\"Automated Tuning\">Automated Tuning</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ccrl.chessdom.com/ccrl/4040/cgi/compare_engines.cgi?family=Deuterium&amp;print=Rating+list&amp;print=Results+table&amp;print=LOS+table&amp;print=Ponder+hit+table&amp;print=Eval+difference+table&amp;print=Comopp+gamenum+table&amp;print=Overlap+table&amp;print=Score+with+common+opponents\">Deuterium</a> in <a href=\"/CCRL\" title=\"CCRL\">CCRL 40/15</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Misc_2\">Misc</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15\" title=\"Edit section: Misc\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deuterium\">Deuterium (heavy hydrogen) from Wikipedia</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deuterium&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Image by <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/User:Alchemist-hp\">Alchemist-hp</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deuterium\">Deuterium (heavy hydrogen) from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#ci